# =====================================================================
# Jackie Lives — .gitignore for the PUBLIC repo
# Goal: publish only SOURCE (code, configs, docs, tools), never the
# copyrighted game audio or large downloaded binaries.
# =====================================================================

# --- COPYRIGHTED GAME AUDIO (CDPR) — must NOT be redistributed --------
# Jackie's voice lines scraped from SoundDB / converted for Audioware.
# These are regenerated locally by tools/scrape_jackie.py + tools/convert_audio.py.
audioware/JackieLives/*.ogg
audioware/JackieLives/*.wav
audioware/JackieLives/*.wem
tools/voice-tagger/audio/
**/recorded_lines.json

# --- COPYRIGHTED DIALOGUE TRANSCRIPTS (CDPR) -------------------------
# Full verbatim dumps of all 777 of Jackie's lines (text). Regenerated by the
# scraper / convert script. lines.sample.json (a tiny example) IS kept.
tools/voice-tagger/lines.json
audioware/JackieLives/index.json

# --- Local Claude Code settings (personal, not shared) ---------------
.claude/settings.local.json

# --- Large downloaded binaries (regenerable, not source) -------------
# portable ffmpeg (~211MB, downloaded by tools/convert_audio.py)
tools/ffmpeg/
tools/ffmpeg.zip

# --- Private / local-only --------------------------------------------
# Claude Code chat history + state (per CLAUDE.md, large + private)
**/documents/Claude_chat_history.md
**/documents/.chat_history_state.json
**/Claude_chat_history.md

# --- Python ----------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/

# --- OS / editors ----------------------------------------------------
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# --- Logs / temp -----------------------------------------------------
*.log
*.tmp

# --- Local-only images (Nexus page art / refs; not source) -----------
jackie.png
mod_thumbnail.png
Jackies_noodles.jpg

# --- Tools (not source; downloaded locally) --------------------------
WolvenKit-*/
WolvenKit*.zip

# --- Built game archives (binary assets; keep repo source-only) ------
*.archive

# COPYRIGHTED transcripts of CDPR VO (like index.json) — never commit
audioware/JackieLives/transcripts.json
audioware/JackieLives/transcripts.txt

# rebuild_bank_yml.py backup of the previous manifest
audioware/JackieLives/*.yml.bak

# R console history (junk)
.Rhistory

# Extracted CDPR quest-graph JSON (datamining artifact, do not redistribute)
docs/research/q005_raw/
docs/research/q101_raw/
# Raw base-game mourning/reaction scene dumps (~222MB of CDPR .scene JSON; local authoring reference only)
docs/mounring_scenes/
